<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(الهدى والنور/٢٨٧/ ١٣: ٠٣: ٠٠)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>